WITH "set_1" AS (SELECT "employee_id" FROM (SELECT "employee_id" FROM "employees" WHERE "manager_id"=1 AND "employee_id"!="manager_id") AS "a"), "set_2" AS (SELECT "c"."employee_id" FROM (SELECT "employee_id" FROM "set_1") AS "b" JOIN (SELECT "employee_id","manager_id" FROM "employees") AS "c" ON "b"."employee_id"="c"."manager_id") SELECT "d"."employee_id" FROM (SELECT "employee_id" FROM "set_2") AS "e" JOIN (SELECT "employee_id","manager_id" FROM "employees") AS "d" ON "d"."manager_id"="e"."employee_id" UNION ALL SELECT "employee_id" FROM "set_2" UNION ALL SELECT "employee_id" FROM "set_1"

WITH "direct" AS (SELECT "employee_id" FROM "Employees" WHERE "manager_id"=1 AND "employee_id" NOT IN (1)), "indirect" AS (SELECT "employee_id" FROM "Employees" WHERE "manager_id" IN (SELECT * FROM "direct")), "2nd_indirect" AS (SELECT "employee_id" FROM "Employees" WHERE "manager_id" IN (SELECT * FROM "indirect")), "final" AS (SELECT "employee_id" FROM "direct" UNION SELECT "employee_id" FROM "indirect") SELECT "employee_id" FROM "final" UNION SELECT "employee_id" FROM "2nd_indirect"
